We have understand that we need to reduce the largest numbers to smallest number possible, we can achieve this by doing division and saving the remainder. Once we have the frequency of smallest numbers possible, we can use them according to the need. 
# Approach
For negative numbers, we have to handle them to get the possible positive number for making the sequence. 
We have to store the remainders with frequency in the map and check against each smallest positivie number possible. 
